==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: outfitted
<hw>outfitted</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>furnished with
essential equipment for a particular occupation or undertaking
occupation; <as>as, a well-<ex>outfitted</ex> expedition to the South
Pole</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fitted out.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Equipped with appropriate wearing apparel and
accessories; <as>as, children properly <ex>outfitted</ex> for
school</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outfitter</ent>⟦br⟧
